{"tid":460301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"放低你鐘意卡通人物比我崩壞","createTime":"2017-11-06T13:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T02:34:09.000Z","uid":157072,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4811126850d9473d21d9b94f1fc7d73d3b263f","tid":460301,"uid":157072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214304_a9e854ab5891d5e78cd1d6547a2352cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214304_a9e854ab5891d5e78cd1d6547a2352cc.jpg&h=cb9eba99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214943_8673cf59f0f2e17466952f11e8fc350f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214943_8673cf59f0f2e17466952f11e8fc350f.jpg&h=6ec8d88c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n本大師曰：最緊要有神綷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559aa290e455b6684fd56116737bf78f6be0df89","tid":460301,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214304_a9e854ab5891d5e78cd1d6547a2352cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214304_a9e854ab5891d5e78cd1d6547a2352cc.jpg&h=cb9eba99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/214943_8673cf59f0f2e17466952f11e8fc350f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F214943_8673cf59f0f2e17466952f11e8fc350f.jpg&h=6ec8d88c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n本大師曰：最緊要有神綷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得個頭開得唔錯 我嗰時有幾個角色都覺得有做反角嘅可能性 但我對哩套戲嘅唔好印象大於好印象<br />\n<br />\n1. 吳彥祖嗰part個人觀感有啲隔硬嚟 甚至覺得有啲多餘 個感覺係導演淨係想用香港啲高樓大廈玩吓災難性層層疊 之後就特登安排佢講個計劃名出嚟咁 有啲唔係好知哩part做乜撚咁<br />\n<br />\n2. 父囡情條線打得唔夠入 感動位覺得有啲尷尬<br />\n<br />\n3. 反角個犯事理由太撚唔合理呱 想炸咗全世界之後做個美國總統 做乜鳩？跟住又係俾人捉到就做5分鐘解說點解佢要犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後嗰句咩 「因為老子就是美國總統！」WTF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係馬後炮 但如果個故事變成美國總統真係背後策劃人 為權力而表面做好人 但暗中搵人阻止男主角 整幾條伏線指向其他角色屈鳩佢哋做反角 而女主角同女船長係總統後後嘅間諜咁 可能會好睇啲<br />\n<br />\nsor 可能太認真 但我真心覺得佢曬咗個idea"},{"pid":"88ad94ecc9a92fe1248c74d9efe1a3f88382fd3b","tid":460301,"uid":39370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"索克天王<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b44975f973b4828028a5d8ce26656da8e6dd55","tid":460301,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"唐老鴨"},{"pid":"20df2906e3d5003345923ead3beb8bb7ce286877","tid":460301,"uid":157072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>索克天王<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/215953_b97946ea300301dc6df277b814d2f7ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F215953_b97946ea300301dc6df277b814d2f7ac.jpg&h=ca36065d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5740b3116310e89fa4ed242ca8e1329781f083dc","tid":460301,"uid":109809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:00:43.000Z","msg":"佐為同光仔"},{"pid":"dd16d06ed61b6db2c91ff030f2b9771be6f4fae8","tid":460301,"uid":72946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"米奇老味"},{"pid":"58ea7382b084ac43250c3a2e15a0c3759f9ed6ea","tid":460301,"uid":39370,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T14:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo